name: Galall
description:
Eighth and final stop of my Interstellar Journey; It looks like donuts - even if I don't like them that much - are a universal dessert, but for some reason, these donuts have shiny sprinkles on them. How do I know? I'm now settled here, serving donuts to empty cars, in front of a never occupied restaurant, getting paid only by the personal satisfaction of tranquility. Sometimes I wonder about the flavor of these donuts, but I'm still too afraid to try them.
